          <section
            _ngcontent-serverapp-c103=""
            class="why_astrology ng-star-inserted"
          >
            <div _ngcontent-serverapp-c103="" class="container">
              <h2
                _ngcontent-serverapp-c103=""
                class="heading_seo_content_headline_chinese_horoscope"
              >
                How Chatting with an astrologer can help you?
              </h2>
              <h3
                _ngcontent-serverapp-c103=""
                class="subheading_why_astrology ng-star-inserted"
              >
                Best online astrology consultation
              </h3>
              <!---->
              <div
                _ngcontent-serverapp-c103=""
                class="why_astrology_hide_and_show ng-star-inserted"
              >
                <p>
                  There’s literally no point in overthinking about your concerns
                  when the solution to them is just a call away. Astrotalk
                  brings to you a pool of over 500+ astrologers with whom you
                  can contact on chat and share with them your problems across
                  all aspects of life including love, finance, Vastu, career,
                  luck, marriage and so on. Simply put, life is a cocktail of
                  highs and lows, and while we enjoy the good times, the bad
                  times, though they teach us a lot, can also leave us worried,
                  depressed and sad. Such times can also hamper the relationship
                  we share with other people in our lives, and we are sure that
                  you wouldn’t want that to happen for yourself.&nbsp;
                </p>

                <p>
                  Astrotalk, with its exceptional astrology consultant services,
                  caters to you the solutions to problems that you might be
                  facing in the aforementioned aspects of life. Some problems in
                  life are simply the consequence of astronomical factors that
                  make it to our fate since the time we are born. To specify,
                  there are some predefined dashas that each one of us has to go
                  through in life. These dashas, like for example, Shani Dasha,
                  or Rahu Dasha, bring all sorts of problems in your life. These
                  problems can lead to loss of confidence, wealth, relationship
                  and other such woes. Thus it is in the best interest to take
                  necessary actions through which such problems can be averted.
                  And astrologers have such solutions for you.&nbsp;
                </p>

                <p>
                  At Astrotalk, we have a pool of learned astrologers with vast
                  experience across various astrology domains like Vedic
                  astrology, Numerology, Tarot reading, Reiki healing, Nandi
                  astrology, Vastu and so on. You can connect with these
                  astrologers and chat with them and ask for solutions to your
                  problems. Astrologers use their experience and astrological
                  knowledge to guide you and help you with the best
                  solutions.&nbsp;
                </p>

                <p>
                  Meanwhile, astrology is not only about solving problems. It
                  also works in many other areas, like if you are planning a
                  wedding and want to find the shubh muhurat for marriage,
                  simply, chat with an astrologer and you will have your answer.
                  Wondering what to name your baby or when to host the mundan
                  ceremony for him/her? Expert astrologers consultation can help
                  here too. Or simply if you are planning to buy a gemstone and
                  wondering what gemstone is made for your rashi? In such
                  circumstances too, chatting with the astrologer can help you
                  find what gemstone would suit your current situation.
                  <a href="https://astrotalk.com/">AstroTalk</a> provides you
                  with the facility to chat with astrologer online free and paid
                  in both ways. To find us online, you just need to search
                  online chat with astrologer or free astro chat or chat with
                  astrologer online free,
                  <a href="https://astrotalk.com/talk-to-astrologer"
                    >talk to astrologer online</a
                  >, and chat with astrologer near me. The aim of our services
                  is to give 100% satisfaction to the users. We offer you many
                  free services as well like
                  <a href="https://astrotalk.com/freekundli">free kundali</a>
                  and
                  <a href="https://astrotalk.com/matchmaking">match making</a>.
                </p>
              </div>

          <section
            _ngcontent-serverapp-c103=""
            class="faqs_about_astrology ng-star-inserted"
          >
            <div _ngcontent-serverapp-c103="" class="container">
              <h2
                _ngcontent-serverapp-c103=""
                class="heading_faqs_about_astrology"
              >
                Chat With Astrologer - FAQs
              </h2>
              <!---->
              <div _ngcontent-serverapp-c103="" class="ng-star-inserted">
                <p>
                  <strong>How can I connect with an astrologer on chat?</strong>
                </p>

                <p>
                  To chat with astrologer online, you simply need to recharge
                  your wallet and find the 'Chat with Astrologer' section on our
                  app or website. Once you click on it, you can choose from
                  hundreds of astrologers you can chat with at your convenience.
                </p>

                <p>
                  <strong
                    >Why do all the astrologers have such good ratings?</strong
                  >
                </p>

                <p>
                  All the astrologers who make it to the Astrotalk platform are
                  categorised across 3 stages. Stage 1 includes astrologers that
                  are highly rated by our customers because of their excellent
                  work. The Stage 2 astrologers are the ones whose ratings fall
                  below fixed criteria. And when that happens, we intentionally
                  remove their profile from the platform so that our customers
                  only get to consult from the top-rated astrologers (Stage 1
                  astrologers). These Stage 2 astrologers are then trained by
                  our expert astrologers, and if they do well during the
                  training, they are brought back on the platform, and if not,
                  they are moved to Stage 3 i.e. they are unrecruited.
                </p>

                <p>
                  Can I chat with the same astrologers I had connected with
                  earlier?
                </p>

                <p>
                  Yes, you can chat with the same astrologers multiple times on
                  our platform. If you wish to chat to the same astrologer,
                  simply find the ‘Order History’ section on the app or the
                  website. Here you will find the list of all the purchases you
                  have made on AstroTalk including your previous chats.
                </p>

                <p>
                  <strong>Will my phone number be kept confidential?</strong>
                </p>

                <p>
                  You really don’t need to use your phone number to chat with
                  astrologer. Also, Astrotalk respects your privacy and as a
                  firm is obliged to keep your information well guarded so no
                  one could ever misuse it whatsoever. You can count on us.
                </p>

                <p>
                  How can I choose the best astrologer to get astrology
                  consultation?
                </p>

                <p>
                  To get astrology consultation through the best astrologer,
                  simply watch out for the rating the other customers may have
                  given to the astrologers. Though we scrutinize all the
                  astrologers ourself and bring onboard only the best ones for
                  you, but as they say, the customer is always right.
                </p>

                <p>
                  <strong
                    >Why some astrologers on the app are so expensive?</strong
                  >
                </p>

                <p>
                  Astrotalk promises the best services to its customers and thus
                  recruits well-experienced astrologers after thorough scrutiny.
                  Most of the astrologers we have onboard entertain an
                  experience of over 10+ years. This is to ensure the
                  predictions or any other information they share with you is
                  based on their broad knowledge, so you always receive accurate
                  information. Also, AstroTalk saves your precious time by
                  helping you consult expert astrologers from the comfort of
                  your home, thus saving your time and money. We maintain strict
                  standards and offer optimum quality. So in a nutshell, our
                  service is qualitative and not expensive.
                </p>

                <p>
                  <strong
                    >Why should I choose Astrotalk for astrology
                    consultation?</strong
                  >
                </p>

                <p>
                  Astrotalk has always worked to offer the best service to its
                  customers, and the result of the same is exceptional ratings
                  and reviews that Astrotalk has garnered on Google, PlayStore,
                  Facebook and other such platforms. It is the successful
                  predictions that have inspired people to leave a good word for
                  us and we continue to live upon that thrust of them.
                </p>

                <p>
                  <strong
                    >Does chatting with an astrologer cost more than talking to
                    an astrologer?</strong
                  >
                </p>

                <p>
                  It simply depends on your and the astrologer’s typing speed.
                  However, if you are not a great talker over a call, then
                  chatting with an astrologer is the best option for you.
                </p>

                <p><strong>How genuine is Astrotalk?</strong></p>

                <p>
                  Genuity can be ensured in two ways. Firstly, from the
                  Astrotalk side, and secondly, from the astrologers' side. And
                  we have got both the areas covered. Astrotalk's prime motive
                  is to give the user the most genuine astrology experience. And
                  to do the same, Astrotalk ensures only the best astrologers
                  make it to the platform. How do we do so? Firstly, before
                  recruiting any new astrologer on Astrotalk, s/he has to go
                  through an interview round conducted by the most experienced
                  astrologers on Astrotalk. This way, we test his/her knowledge
                  of astrology before they are able to interact with the users.
                  Secondly, a team of astrologers is always present to train the
                  astrologers from time to time and help them in learning new
                  skills. And thirdly, users are motivated to rate the
                  astrologers after every session, so that they can be judged
                  accordingly. If the astrologer's rating falls below 4-star, he
                  or she is taken down. This is one of the ways we adopt to
                  ensure Astrotalk is the most genuine platform for you to talk
                  to astrologers. It is these steps due to which we are able to
                  secure a good rating across all major rating platforms such as
                  Google, Play Store, etc.
                </p>
              </div>

Traditionally these zodiac animals were used to date the years.&q;:&q;The Chinese animal zodiac, or shengxiao (/shnng-sshyaoww/ ‘born resembling’), is a repeating cycle of 12 years, with each year being represented by an animal and its reputed attributes. Traditionally these zodiac animals were used to date the years.&q;,&q;The Chinese Zodiac, known as Sheng Xiao, is based on a twelve-year cycle, each year in that cycle related to an animal sign. These signs are the rat, ox, tiger, rabbit, dragon, snake, horse, sheep, monkey, rooster, dog and pig. It is calculated according to Chinese lunar calendar. You can use the zodiac calculator to search for your Chinese zodiac animal sign. Now, for example, if the planet Rahu is in the house of finance in your kundli, you may be overspending unnecessarily or simply finding it tough to accumulate wealth. However, if the planet Sun is in the house of finances, it may bring you enormous gains in business or even at your job. The effects of each planet on your horoscope simply depend on your karma and the character of the planet. Now we shall discuss these one-by-one.&q;,&q;Panchang Tithi&q;:&q;Panchang Tithi&q;,&q;Tithi is one of the elements of Hindu panchang. It is very important to know the Tithi to find the Shubh Muhurat. A Tithi is the duration of two phases of the Moon that are observed from the Earth. As per astrology, there are as many as 30 Tithis in a month. Out of these, 15 fall in Shukla Paksha and the remaining 15 in the Krishna paksha. A tithi begins from one sunrise and continues till the other sunrise.&q;:&q;Tithi is one of the elements of Hindu panchang. It is very important to know the Tithi to find the Shubh Muhurat. A Tithi is the duration of two phases of the Moon that are observed from the Earth. As per astrology, there are as many as 30 Tithis in a month. Out of these, 15 fall in Shukla Paksha and the remaining 15 in the Krishna paksha. A tithi begins from one sunrise and continues till the other sunrise.&q;,&q;However, at some times, two dates may fall on the same day. Of these, the tithi which does not see the sunrise is called the Kshya titihi and the one which lasts till two sunrise is called Vrishy tithi.&q;:&q;However, at some times, two dates may fall on the same day. Of these, the tithi which does not see the sunrise is called the Kshya titihi and the one which lasts till two sunrise is called Vrishy tithi.&q;,&q;Here are the names of Krishna Paksha and Shukla Paksha:&q;:&q;Here are the names of Krishna Paksha and Shukla Paksha:&q;,&q;Krishna Paksha tithis - &q;:&q;Krishna Paksha tithis - &q;,&q;Pratipada, Dwitiya, Tritiya, Chaturthi, Panchami, Shashti, Saptami, Ashtami, Navami, Dashami, Ekadashi, Dwadashi, Trayodashi, Chaturdashi, Amavasya&q;:&q; Pratipada, Dwitiya, Tritiya, Chaturthi, Panchami, Shashti, Saptami, Ashtami, Navami, Dashami, Ekadashi, Dwadashi, Trayodashi, Chaturdashi, Amavasya&q;,&q;Shukla Paksha tithis - &q;:&q;Shukla Paksha tithis - &q;,&q;Pratipada, Dwitiya, Tritiya, Chaturthi, Panchami, Shashti, Saptami, Ashtami, Navami, Dashami, Ekadashi, Dwadashi, Trayodashi, Chaturdashi, Poornima&q;:&q;Pratipada, Dwitiya, Tritiya, Chaturthi, Panchami, Shashti, Saptami, Ashtami, Navami, Dashami, Ekadashi, Dwadashi, Trayodashi, Chaturdashi, Poornima&q;,&q;Vaar&q;:&q;Vaar&q;,&q;The second important thing when it comes to finding the Shubh muhurat 2022 is Vaar. Whatever constellation is the Moon passing through at a particular point in time becomes the Nakshatra for the day. Back in the times of Sages, though they knew of zodiac signs, however, for better clarity, they divided the 12 zodiac signs into 27 nakshatras. Each Nakshatra is approximately a day long and has its own characteristics. While some nakshatras are good for a particular task. Others, on the other hand, may not be good. Thus when finding out the Shubh Muhurat in 2022 you must only abide by a muhurat that falls on good nakshatra.&q;:&q;Nakshatras are nothing but constellations that we see in the sky. your kundli report&q;:&q;Share your kundli report&q;,&q;Ashtakvarga is used to assess the strength and patterns that are present in a birth chart. The Ashtakvarga or Ashtakavarga is a numerical quantification or score of each planet placed in the chart with reference to the other 7 planets and the Lagna. In Sarva Ashtaka Varga the total scores of all the BAVs are overlaid and then totalled. This makes the SAV of the chart. The total of all the scores should be 337.&q;:&q;Ashtakvarga is used to assess the strength and patterns that are present in a birth chart. The Ashtakvarga or Ashtakavarga is a numerical quantification or score of each planet placed in the chart with reference to the other 7 planets and the Lagna. In Sarva Ashtaka Varga the total scores of all the BAVs are overlaid and then totalled. This makes the SAV of the chart.
